sub_title: People, Leadership & Culture Strategist | Diversity & Inclusion Consultant | Conflict Management Specialist | Lawyer | ICF Certified Coach | Speaker | Board Director | C-Suite Advisor | Best Selling Author
summary:
I have helped transform Fortune 500 companies in Asia, Europe, and North America as a leadership development strategist, culture builder, executive coach, conflict resolution specialist, trainer, and program manager.

I deliver industry-leading results in learning and development, people management, and diversity and inclusion. I am a trusted business advisor and have extensive global experience in client leadership, business development, and P&L responsibilities.

With over 19 years of client and project leadership experience, I have a master's degree in Law and Business from the University of Virginia and the Indian School of Business respectively. I have worked as an attorney at law for seven years in the U.S. with a license to practice law in India and U.S. I am an ICF-certified executive coach, trainer, negotiator, and mediator.

I am an award-winning public speaker, bestselling author, and executive coach who is a passionate mentor and advocate of sustainability, diversity, and inclusion.
 
Areas of Expertise
People and Culture Strategy; Learning & Development; Sustainable Development, Diversity, Equity, Inclusion & Belonging; Employee Engagement; Conflict Management; Policy, Ethics, and Governance
